msgstr "任务6：数据流任务：加载到MySQL"

#: .\pipeline\templates\pipeline\ssis.html:958
msgid "เชื่อมลูกศรจาก Log Transform Time → Load to MySQL"
msgstr "连接箭头从Log Transform Time → Load to MySQL"

